text = "In front of you, your ranks meet those of the enemy. It is very loud. There is a lot of screaming. There's other sounds, too, but the screaming seems the loudest.

You are supposed to be watching the soldier in front of you. You swallow. It is very hard to concentrate, but it's important that you watch the soldier in front of you. You need to be ready, in case he rotates out, or in case he falls. It is important that you be ready, or he might stumble back into you and then you might fall, and if you might fall you might die, and you don't want to die. You definitely don't want to die.

\"Rotating!\" cries the soldier in front of you. You swallow and prepare to replace him.
"
